     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN52
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     RRN1
      * HEADER
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    MC
     C           1         DO   4         X       30
     C           MCN,X     IFNE *BLANK
     C           '#'       CAT  MCN,X:0   MC,X
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     W@YYMM  60
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     BT
     C                     CLEARSFL01
